= Culture & Collaboration =

(% class="box infomessage" %)
(((
**FactHarbor combines human values, structured decision-making, and automation to build a high-trust environment.**
We use **Sociocracy 3.0** (Consent pattern) to maintain high velocity and ensure empowerment, iterative learning, and data-driven transparency.

🔗 **Project Repository:** [[FactHarbor on GitHub>>https://github.com/robertschaub/FactHarbor]]
)))

